Control, and Max Payne\u003c/em\u003e—tend to be single player, third-person, linear adventures with cutscenes, lots of dialogue, and endings. \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/fbc-firebreak-control-2-alan-wake-remedy-coop-shooter-1851675403\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/fbc-firebreak-control-2-alan-wake-remedy-coop-shooter-1851675403\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eFBC: Firebreak\u003c/em\u003e isn’t like those past games at all\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. And while it might disappoint some Remedy fans, I’m excited to see the studio doing something so different.  - Zack Zwiezen \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/fbc-firebreak-remedy-co-op-fomo-live-service-preview-1851771133\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/fbc-firebreak-remedy-co-op-fomo-live-service-preview-1851771133\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93\" data-recommend-id=\"image://a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2996\" data-height=\"1682\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A green N64 sits in a box. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A green N64 sits in a box. \" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A green N64 sits in a box. \" data-chomp-id=\"a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1682\" data-alt=\"A green N64 sits in a box. \" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto: Joe Raedle\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93\" data-recommend-id=\"image://a8d616e8b4c29846d994af87db6a8b93\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2996\" data-height=\"1682\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A green N64 sits in a box. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe’re in the midst of a retro console revolution. Between emulation handhelds \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/ayn-odin-2-mini-ayaneo-pocket-dmg-micro-emulation-1851488370\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/ayn-odin-2-mini-ayaneo-pocket-dmg-micro-emulation-1851488370\"\u003epouring out of China\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e and more affordable FPGA consoles \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;External link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://www.timeextension.com/news/2025/01/taki-udons-fpga-ps1-is-called-superstation-one-pre-orders-start-at-usd149-this-week\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://www.timeextension.com/news/2025/01/taki-udons-fpga-ps1-is-called-superstation-one-pre-orders-sta